{"tid":2354033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"之鋒口訊：要維繫香港人呢個身份，廣東歌真係好重要","createTime":"2021-01-05T07:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T10:48:14.000Z","uid":212249,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cd090357fb5beaa453cb85a261f0f5a13fd3166e","tid":2354033,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:40:45.000Z","msg":"編輯：新年伊始，之鋒託探訪親友傳來口訊，祝福各位香港人新年進步，希望各位新一年毋忘初心，互相守望。<br />\n獄中的聖誕和新年儘管寒冷難捱，還幸有牆外的書信聊作寄託。令他驚喜的是，今年的《叱咤》頒獎禮收穫不少關注，他又覺得「撐姜」、「撐Mirror」與否、心儀歌手有否獲獎其實不是最重要，最重要的是愈來愈多人重新討論香港樂壇，令「香港人撐廣東歌」成為主流。<br />\n之鋒又笑說在入獄之前比較忙碌，沒有太多時間聽歌，反而入獄後才有機會間中聽聽電台節目。聽着收音機的歌聲，又會惦記着牆內牆外的大家。然後忽然又會想，其實不單是身處香港的人，就算是對於鐵窗內的人、流落異鄉的人，廣東歌真的很重要。<br />\n云云書信當中，朋友所抄的兩首歌詞令他印象深刻，一首是林二汶的《再聚》，另一首是是KOLOR的《可再遇見》，望與牆外的大家分享。<br />\n圖片：林二汶 《再聚》封面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/134035090_3636488596443622_2622360114654389836_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=lelyohj4lxYAX_KRhYH&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=bd980fd5208fe24a45e2eee67003a2c3&amp;oe=601A060D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F134035090_3636488596443622_2622360114654389836_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3Dlelyohj4lxYAX_KRhYH%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3Dbd980fd5208fe24a45e2eee67003a2c3%26oe%3D601A060D&h=e56b4866&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"439dfe63167eddb826bd7c6705d3591c72c85014","tid":2354033,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ec0482ab40f7cde6994c13ec432c46d418d8b1","tid":2354033,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.564294826996363/3636488593110289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fphotos%2Fa.564294826996363%2F3636488593110289%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=36028543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.564294826996363/3636488593110289/</a>"},{"pid":"ead45363019b64b0d067231d58fb90c8a7b415f9","tid":2354033,"uid":37869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"歌影視真係幾重要<br />\n就算tvb蝕住拍劇冇人睇都係好事"},{"pid":"bfb5df4aaccc5495227546ed93806f251ce06b40","tid":2354033,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:53:44.000Z","msg":"[本土歌影視業與心態] 不要問香港有冇好音樂，要問你有冇支持過做好音樂的人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2354046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2354046</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>經常有個比喻，美斯生於香港也可能踢不成波，填鴨教育下做了外賣步兵，但你要問自己，當美斯在追夢踢傑志的時候，你有冇買飛入場睇波？令他不用當外賣員。<br />\n<br />\n當本土的好音樂出現了，你有否珍惜，珍惜仍在唱廣東話，特別是有良知的樂團。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"473fd485331003c827e23909d01f2de75a4af5f5","tid":2354033,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c6a53e8f20ce09ca0376ccf05f04ab679f80b58","tid":2354033,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"但係歌詞冇意思之餘又難聽呢"},{"pid":"e52c5ae7649383dd67ddbba329d019bfdd821f32","tid":2354033,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"#drum#pi"},{"pid":"80291a31aa21d4530de3f187c71eed104f51012b","tid":2354033,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ead45363019b64b0d067231d58fb90c8a7b415f9","tid":2354033,"uid":37869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:52:08.000Z","msg":"歌影視真係幾重要<br />\n就算tvb蝕住拍劇冇人睇都係好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"呢樣真，當年TVB一個保埋廣州嘅廣東話<br />\n但副作用係當地人口音變左香港音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /